Rogue, Test Server
</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub2.ezboard.com/ufiae.showPublicProfile>Fiae</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://home.pacifier.com/~load/EQ000030.jpg BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Global user</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/27/00 1:57:34 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://home.pacifier.com/~load/EQ000030.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Blackburrow</span><hr size=1> *arches an elvish eyebrow* <br>
